+### Trade history
+
+```csharp
+IReadOnlyList<Trade> myTrades = await client.Account.GetTradeHistoryAsync(
+    new Symbol(Asset.Btc, Asset.Usdt),
+    limit: 100,
+    startTime: DateTimeOffset.UtcNow.AddDays(-30));
